stats.note: HJ vs UTG: Tight 3bet, call with strong hands in position
CO vs UTG: Tight 3bet, wider call range
BTN vs UTG: Value 3bet, wide call with position
BTN vs HJ: Value 3bet + blocker, very wide call
BTN vs CO: Wide 3bet with blockers, very wide call
SB vs UTG: 3bet or fold (no call OOP)
SB vs CO: Wide 3bet or fold
SB vs BTN: Very wide 3bet or fold
BB vs UTG: Tight 3bet, wide call to defend
BB vs HJ: Medium 3bet, wide call
BB vs CO: Wide 3bet, very wide call
BB vs BTN: Very wide 3bet, widest call
BB vs SB: Blind war, widest ranges
